These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, handball, baseball
1. the person who's sport is handball is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | fanta | water | tea   |
| Sport      | badminton    | handball  | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, juice
There are 3 different nationalities: german, american, japanese
1. the german is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the american is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | water     | juice      |
| Nationality   | american | german | japanese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, cola
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, peach, cauliflower
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | cola  | sprite       |
| Food       | strawberry     | peach | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, nectarine, kiwi
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, hiking
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | kiwi    | nectarine     | pineapple |
| Hobby   | hiking | camping | dancing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, boat, tram
1. the person driving the boat is the owner of the horse##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the owner of the goat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | turtle | goat     | horse |
| Transport   | tram        | bike | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, artichoke, potato
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, bike, quad-bike
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person eating potato is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | potato | peach      | artichoke  |
| Transport   | van       | bike | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, house, techno
3 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, mouse
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of house is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | d&b     | house    |
| Pet           | lizard | mouse | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, eggplant, lemon
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person eating eggplant is the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | lemon | pineapple | eggplant      |
| Hobby   | board-games     | sudoku | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, video-games
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, mouse
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games  |
| Pet     | mouse     | chinchilla      | hedgehog |

