.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, mirinda
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, action, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | juice   | almond-milk    | mirinda    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | spy | satire |

