There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, italian, turkish
1. the fan of soul is the japanese##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the turkish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | soul   | jazz  |
| Nationality   | turkish    | japanese | italian |

