.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, apple, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, software-developer
1. the electrician is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
3. the coach is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | avocado     | carrot   | apple     |
| Job    | software-developer | electrician | coach |

