.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, metal, blues
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | tea | hot-chocolate  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | blues   | techno |

