There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian
1. the indian is on the far left##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
3. the brazilian is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | lawyer | analyst | entrepreneur |
| Nationality   | indian  | brazilian      | french |

