1. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | card-games | fishing | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | blues | metal     | d&b  |

