.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, cabbage, nectarine
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | nectarine | kale       | cabbage  |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | lacrosse | basketball |

 